- Keep it under 120 words — this is going via email
- Warm and human, not corporate or scripted
- IMPORTANT: Use the research data above to directly answer questions about schools, walkability, and market conditions. For property-specific questions not in the details or research above (HOA fees, roof age, inspection items, basement, lot size), do NOT guess — acknowledge briefly and say you'll follow up.

Return ONLY the message text. No labels, no subject line, no formatting markers.

